post_content: Better-than-basic sleeveless V-neck/V-back tank top in the softest, smoothest jersey we could find, from fashion-forward brand Silence + Noise. In a drapey stretch fit finished with an elongated hem + skinny spaghetti straps. UO exclusive.

Sleeveless pleated high-neck swing cami with a super strappy by Kimchi Blue. In accordion-pleat chiffon with a chic loose fit that tapers out to the bottom, finished with a low back with caged straps topped with a button closure. Available only at UO.
